title: Contacts
description: Connect with NexusOS through social media, e-mail, or phone number. We're here to assist you!

body.raw:
<Callout>
  Feel free to reach out to us anytime. We're here to assist you with any questions or inquiries you may have.
</Callout>

### Developer Contact

| Contact  | Details                            |
| -------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Address  | Rajshahi, Bangladesh               |
| Email    | official.rudrodipsarker@gmail.com  |
| Phone    | +8801778881194                     |

### Social Media

| Social Media  | Profile URL                                                      |
| ------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Twitter/X     | [twitter](https://twitter.com/rds_agi)                           |
| LinkedIn      | [linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/in/rudrodip-sarker-964392262)|
| Discord       | [discord](https://discordapp.com/users/841126921886498817)       |


### Support and Inquiries

For support, inquiries, or any other information, please reach out to us via e-mail or phone. We value your feedback and look forward to assisting you.

Thank you for connecting with NexusOS!
